summary: A Compilation of Graphical Re-Texture Mods that Bring a Level of Beauty and Immersion to Skyrim That is Enough to Literally Take Your Breath Away.
descriptionHtml:
::I AM NOT A MODDER::
All Mods Included in This Compilation Have Their Original Authors Posted in The ReadMe.

Do you HATE the High Res Texture Pack from Bethesda?
Me Too!
Because of this i have done my best to create a comprehensive compilation effecting all of the most important textures in the game.
To me, this compilation is unparalleled in both beauty and performance.
All of these mods can be found on their original mod page, by the original author. 
(Links in ReadMe. If  you wish to utilize part(s) of this compilation, please use the original mod page as the compilation is simply a Data folder containing all mods and newest patches/updates, pre-allocated to in their correct spot.)
author: Various Authors
